Speedyseek allows you fastest access to Yahoo’s results by changing your search settings.

Powered by Yahoo’s powerful search engine, Speedyseek improves your browsing experience and delivers the most relevant results straight to your browser.

Speedyseek will bring your browsing and internet searching experience to the next level, in the fastest possible way. 

By clicking "Add to chrome", I accept and agree to installing SpeedySeek extension and setting Chrome™ New Tab and default search to that provided by the service and the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. The extension will update your search settings and will change your New Tab and default search services provided by Yahoo.

Features:
A search box integrated in your browsing experience
